text: Muhammad Zainal Haq (born 5 April 1992) is an Indonesian professional footballer who plays as a defender for Liga 2 club Mitra Kukar. ==Career== In January 2011, Zainal Haq joined Peñarol, Besides Zainal, Penarol signed two other players, namely Manahati Lestusen, and Abdul Lestaluhu. Demis Djamaoeddin (Deportivo Indonesia manager) said "They are already there, and introduced to the public".5 pemain muda Indonesia berlaga di Uruguay dan Chili Currently, he is still on loan at Penarol.Penarol ingin kontrak permanen Zainal Haq ===C.S. Visé=== Zainal joined Belgian club C.S. Visé. As reported on the official website of Vise, as part of the Bakrie Group project in April 2011, Vise welcomed three main players of Deportivo Indonesia.Lagi, Tiga pemain indonesia gabung CS Visé ===Persebaya Bhayangkara=== Zainal Haq joined Persebaya (Bhayangkara) in 2014 Inter Island Cup. Persebaya Bhayangkara bring 26 players to Kediri for the pre-season tournament Inter Island Cup (IIC) in 2014.
